metadata.name: kiss
metadata.description:
“kiss” which we can describe as touching our lips to a person or object or perhaps a little “vacuuming” audibly, is a human action that has countless meanings in all kinds of cultures. although love and passion come to mind first, it has many other meanings such as sincerity, respect, submission.

"if I kissed you once, the two feel hurt..if I wanted to kiss you twice, the third one's neck would be bent.."
